1. Create a socket
2. Bind the socket (IP, Pnt)
3. Configure --> listening socket
4. Want for client to connect
5.--> client-socket is available
6. When a client connects, the socket library creates a new socket for communicating with the client
7. Read the client messages. What does the client want? (metho rcv)
8. Process the request and send a response message (method send)